lead_paragraph: The broad market moved higher, focused on quarterly earnings that, while healthy, were contained by the strength of the dollar.

headline.print_headline: Nasdaq Tops the Nominal High Set During the 2000 Bubble
headline.main: Modest Gain for Market, and a Milestone for the Nasdaq

snippet: The broad market moved higher, focused on quarterly earnings that, while healthy, were contained by the strength of the dollar.
abstract: Stocks rise as Nasdaq hits nominal record high of 5,056.06, exceeding peak it achieved at apex of dot-com bubble fifteen years earlier.
